{"tid":1283961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[世紀大和解]我地終於得到藍絲認同","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:47:21.000Z","uid":264872,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8317c3c4bda826e19ac7be984865a90577cb2759","tid":1283961,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"一次咁大把<br />\n<br />\n周融本身想借光復屯公插我方一刀<br />\n點知呢個議題命中咗港豬「燒到埋嚟先關我事」嘅心態<br />\n光復屯公活動大獲好評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LmyqiM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LmyqiM.png&h=cc83dfd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbxxFTD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbxxFTD.png&h=f78333d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEFOYFi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEFOYFi.png&h=c3018a72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXUW7yE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXUW7yE.png&h=d0b5b8ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68H50TE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68H50TE.png&h=6f2ff51d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyywWr0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyywWr0.png&h=392e72fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TomuH60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTomuH60.png&h=5304c90d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝屯公阿伯嘅咸濕促成今次和解<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zs9H8k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zs9H8k.png&h=eac978e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔第一次quote post，細力啲屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然佢哋要拮到肉先知痛，不如我哋投其所好，喺一啲意見訴求相同嘅議題上（民生、強姦金、食物安全、交通） 幫佢哋（同時亦都係幫自己人）發聲、爭取應得權利。<br />\n差佬、區議員、正苦唔做/hea做嘅事，就由我哋幫手發聲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望可以改變淺藍人對我哋嘅偏見，明白我哋真係愛香港 為大家做實事，而唔係鳩融之流黐label話我哋淨係識「搞搞震」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加可以推進年青力量議政+落區，同保皇黨蛇齋餅糭抗衡（雖然無水喉 一定唔夠抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但起碼make Noise ，做實事）<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n利申 新會然 非三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c10c04e12ed08b04b9bb65369f87e2fd8153ad","tid":1283961,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8317c3c4bda826e19ac7be984865a90577cb2759","tid":1283961,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"一次咁大把<br />\n<br />\n周融本身想借光復屯公插我方一刀<br />\n點知呢個議題命中咗港豬「燒到埋嚟先關我事」嘅心態<br />\n光復屯公活動大獲好評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LmyqiM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LmyqiM.png&h=cc83dfd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbxxFTD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbxxFTD.png&h=f78333d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEFOYFi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEFOYFi.png&h=c3018a72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXUW7yE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXUW7yE.png&h=d0b5b8ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68H50TE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68H50TE.png&h=6f2ff51d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyywWr0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyywWr0.png&h=392e72fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T